we have created the clone presented on the screen in the competition using html css , there are three different sections :
one was the main page another two were profile and project , we have used different properties of css and html to do it .
to achieve the purpose we have used paper and pen to draw the skeleton of the shown site and then we just followed the direction given by team members.
we have used flex box, colour gradient and other properties of the css and html , we transversed through one page to another using anchor tag and the path or the name of the other file.
we have completed as a group under the given deadline.
